@startuml
title Horizon Bank customer-acquisition value stream cross-map

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ranksep 18
skinparam nodesep 8
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowFontColor #1E293B
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
  RoundCorner 8
}

rectangle "STAKEHOLDER\nRetail Customer\nNeed: establish a banking relationship\n[seeks value through value stream]" as CUSTOMER #E0F2FE
rectangle "VALUE STREAM\nAcquire customer relationship\n[comprises five value stages]" as STREAM #DBEAFE

rectangle "VALUE-STAGE BAND\nEach stage contributes\nindependently to Outcome" as SH #E0F2FE
rectangle "LOCAL-CAPABILITY BAND\nCapabilities enable\nthe aligned stage" as CH #E0E7FF
rectangle "BIAN-REFERENCE BAND\nBIAN informs responsibility\nanalysis for the aligned stage" as BH #F1F5F9

rectangle "1  Need understood\nSuitable direction is clear\n[contributes to Outcome]" as S1 #F8FAFC
rectangle "2  Application established\nIntent and evidence can proceed\n[contributes to Outcome]" as S2 #F8FAFC
rectangle "3  Identity and eligibility confirmed\nGoverned decision is supported\n[contributes to Outcome]" as S3 #FEF3C7
rectangle "4  Banking relationship established\nAuthoritative relationship records exist\n[contributes to Outcome]" as S4 #F8FAFC
rectangle "5  Services ready to use\nAgreed service can be used\n[contributes to Outcome]" as S5 #F8FAFC

rectangle "Primary: Relationship Management\nSupporting: Digital Servicing" as C1 #E0E7FF
rectangle "Primary: Document Capture\nSupporting: Digital Servicing" as C2 #E0E7FF
rectangle "Primary: Identity Verification\nand Risk Assessment\nSupporting: Financial Crime Screening" as C3 #E0E7FF
rectangle "Primary: Party Management\nand Account Opening\nSupporting: none in selected view" as C4 #E0E7FF
rectangle "Primary: Digital Servicing\nSupporting: Notification Management\nand Account Servicing" as C5 #E0E7FF

rectangle "BIAN 14.0 logical reference\nAssess candidate Service Domains\nand interactions" as B1 #F1F5F9
rectangle "BIAN 14.0 logical reference\nAssess candidate Service Domains\nand interactions" as B2 #F1F5F9
rectangle "BIAN 14.0 logical reference\nAssess candidate Service Domains\nand interactions" as B3 #F1F5F9
rectangle "BIAN 14.0 logical reference\nAssess candidate Service Domains\nand interactions" as B4 #F1F5F9
rectangle "BIAN 14.0 logical reference\nAssess candidate Service Domains\nand interactions" as B5 #F1F5F9

rectangle "OUTCOME\nUsable banking relationship" as OUTCOME #DCFCE7

CUSTOMER -[hidden]down- STREAM
STREAM -[hidden]down- SH

SH -[hidden]right- CH
CH -[hidden]right- BH
SH -[hidden]down- S1
CH -[hidden]down- C1
BH -[hidden]down- B1
S1 -[hidden]down- S2
S2 -[hidden]down- S3
S3 -[hidden]down- S4
S4 -[hidden]down- S5
C1 -[hidden]down- C2
C2 -[hidden]down- C3
C3 -[hidden]down- C4
C4 -[hidden]down- C5
B1 -[hidden]down- B2
B2 -[hidden]down- B3
B3 -[hidden]down- B4
B4 -[hidden]down- B5
S1 -[hidden]right- C1
S2 -[hidden]right- C2
S3 -[hidden]right- C3
S4 -[hidden]right- C4
S5 -[hidden]right- C5
C1 -[hidden]right- B1
C2 -[hidden]right- B2
C3 -[hidden]right- B3
C4 -[hidden]right- B4
C5 -[hidden]right- B5
S5 -[hidden]down- OUTCOME
C5 -[hidden]down- OUTCOME
B5 -[hidden]down- OUTCOME

note bottom
  Row alignment expresses mapping, not process sequence.
  BIAN mappings are candidate, partial and many-to-many.
  A Service Domain is not a value stage, process step, application or microservice.
end note
@enduml
